{"word":"G4975 - σχεδόν - schedón - skhed-on' - Almost","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σχεδόν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">schedón</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">skhed-on'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Almost</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கொஞ்சங்குறைய - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. near, hard by"},{"paragraph":"2. well - nigh, nearly, almost"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed derivative of the alternate of <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a> as an adverb; <i>nigh</i>, that is, <i>nearly:</i> - almost.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}